questions.quote: Isn't it funny how we kept running into each other? It's as if someone really wants us to be together.
Unbelievable! I mean you really kept Joey's underwear?! Why? Why would you do that?!
You're just so mean to each other! And I don't want to end up like that with Rachel. I still like you!
Pheebs, this guy has been obsessed with your sister, for God knows how long, okay, you don't just give up something like that.
No, it's just that he got this new like home theater dealie, and he wants y'know, us to check it out.
Yes! Didn't you ever read Sports Illustrated?! No! I didn't read yours! But come on, we can go to the game tonight!
So, I got us some reservations for Sunday night, okay? How about, Ernie's at 9 o'clock?
Oh my God, honey we are so meant to be together. We both have copies of the Annie soundtrack.
Well, who cares what your Mom thinks? So you pulled a Monica.
So tell me something, is leaving the Christmas lights up part of your plan to keep us merry all year long?
